    <div class="Combat">
        <h1>Combat</h1>
        <p>Xero will feature a character-action based combat</p>
        <h2>Grades</h2>
        <p>Your combat preformance is graded at the end of major battles, using letters A-E, alongside S </p>
        <h2>Grades meaning</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>E - bare minimum</li>
            <li>D - Died less than 3 times during the fight, used less than 10 items</li>
            <li>C - Died at least once, used less than 8 items</li>
            <li>B - Didn't die during the entire fight, used a total of 5 items</li>
            <li>A - Didn't die the entire fight, didn't use any items</li>
            <li>S - Didn't get hit the enire fight</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>More details about your combat tools</h2>
        <h3>Weapons</h3>
        <p>Each playable character can equip 4 different weapons out of the 50 available weapons, and switch between them using the rear touchpad</p>
        <p>Switching between weapons will also make the character use a special weapon switching attack</p>
        <p>The game features 10 distinct weapon types, with each type featuring a total of 5 weapons under it</p>
        <h3>Potentia</h3>
        <p>The main power system of Xero - a potentia is a person's conciousness manifested into a magic abillity</p>
        <p>Some characters can swap their potentia, but have lower magic or strength stats, while some can't but have full magic and physical powers</p>
        <p>There's also a 1/8b chance for a person to both be able to swap potentia and have full magic / physical strength</p>
        <p>Gameplay-wise, you activate a potentia abillity by pressing the O button, usually you can aslo equip 4 potentia at a time, and swap between them using the d-pad</p>
        <h3>Magic / Magic Manipulation / Magic Fusion</h3>
        <p>Another tools you get is standard magic, which swap out your O skill for the magic attack you used for a certain emounts of uses</p>
        <p>Magic  manipulation allows you to imbude the chosen element with your charged attacks by holding down the attack buttons after a combo</p>
        <p>Magic Fusion allows you to fuse two magic elements to create a new one and use it either as normal magic or magic manipulation</p>
    </div>
    
